{"lastModified":1761921453986,"uri":"c::8275378522::vessel::5dc90960-dcf1-11ef-a54d-2d129dec3260","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Caribbean Virgin Islands (US/BVI), Caribbean Leewards, Caribbean Windwards\n\nBERESHIT is a 15.24m / 50ft Catamaran Luxury Yacht built in 2023 by Leopard. Sleeping 8 guests in 4 cabins and with a crew of 2. Cruising at 7.00 kn/ph with a top speed of 18.00 kn/ph. The guest cabins comprise of 4 cabins with a double bed and en-suite bathroom facilities.","blueprint":{"name":"BERESHIT","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::5dc90960-dcf1-11ef-a54d-2d129dec3260::assets::5d78dba0-dcf3-11ef-82dc-7159f8120ef0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5dc90960-dcf1-11ef-a54d-2d129dec3260::assets::4c433010-dcf3-11ef-82dc-7159f8120ef0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5dc90960-dcf1-11ef-a54d-2d129dec3260::assets::4c45c820-dcf3-11ef-82dc-7159f8120ef0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5dc90960-dcf1-11ef-a54d-2d129dec3260::assets::4c6efb00-dcf3-11ef-82dc-7159f8120ef0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5dc90960-dcf1-11ef-a54d-2d129dec3260::assets::4c3a2f60-dcf3-11ef-82dc-7159f8120ef0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5dc90960-dcf1-11ef-a54d-2d129dec3260::assets::4c6d9b70-dcf3-11ef-82dc-7159f8120ef0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5dc90960-dcf1-11ef-a54d-2d129dec3260::assets::4c6f4920-dcf3-11ef-82dc-7159f8120ef0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5dc90960-dcf1-11ef-a54d-2d129dec3260::assets::4c474ec0-dcf3-11ef-82dc-7159f8120ef0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5dc90960-dcf1-11ef-a54d-2d129dec3260::assets::4c5de400-dcf3-11ef-82dc-7159f8120ef0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5dc90960-dcf1-11ef-a54d-2d129dec3260::assets::4c4700a0-dcf3-11ef-82dc-7159f8120ef0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5dc90960-dcf1-11ef-a54d-2d129dec3260::assets::4c479ce0-dcf3-11ef-82dc-7159f8120ef0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5dc90960-dcf1-11ef-a54d-2d129dec3260::assets::4c6f9740-dcf3-11ef-82dc-7159f8120ef0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5dc90960-dcf1-11ef-a54d-2d129dec3260::assets::4c70a8b0-dcf3-11ef-82dc-7159f8120ef0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5dc90960-dcf1-11ef-a54d-2d129dec3260::assets::4c4b9480-dcf3-11ef-82dc-7159f8120ef0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5dc90960-dcf1-11ef-a54d-2d129dec3260::assets::4c48fc70-dcf3-11ef-82dc-7159f8120ef0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5dc90960-dcf1-11ef-a54d-2d129dec3260::assets::4c3bdd10-dcf3-11ef-82dc-7159f8120ef0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5dc90960-dcf1-11ef-a54d-2d129dec3260::assets::4c383390-dcf3-11ef-82dc-7159f8120ef0/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::5dc90960-dcf1-11ef-a54d-2d129dec3260::assets::4c5be830-dcf3-11ef-82dc-7159f8120ef0/{imageVariant}"],"make":"Leopard","maxCrew":2,"sleeps":8,"basePort":{"uri":"a::place::4b399df0-78f2-11ee-9d9d-cfe908b4a777","name":"Yacht Haven Grande","coordinates":{"latitude":18.33640830795738,"longitude":-64.92014313558178},"country":"US Virgin Islands"},"builtYear":2023,"topSpeed":18,"cruiseSpeed":7,"cabinLayout":[{"label":"Double Cabin","value":"4"}],"cabins":4,"bathrooms":4,"decks":2,"length":15.24,"beam":7.92,"draft":2.59,"engines":"2 X Yanmar 85 HP","amenities":[{"label":"Salon Stereo"},{"label":"Device Hookups"},{"label":"Deck Shower"},{"label":"Water Maker"},{"label":"Salon TV"},{"label":"Hammock"},{"label":"BBQ"},{"label":"Inverter"},{"label":"Onboard WIFI"},{"label":"Children Allowed"}],"toys":[{"label":"Dinghy 6+1pax"},{"label":"Snorkel Gear"},{"label":"SU Paddle Boards"},{"label":"Tube"},{"label":"Kayaks 1 Pax"},{"label":"Beach Games"},{"label":"Swim Platform"},{"label":"Fishing Gear"}],"entertainment":["Salon Stereo","Device Hookups","Salon TV","Onboard WIFI"]},"crew":[{"name":"Pablo Gomez Gonzalez","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::5dc90960-dcf1-11ef-a54d-2d129dec3260::assets::d5aa5140-dcf2-11ef-8280-31b82e11793d/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"With over four years of experience as a professional sailor and three years as a skilled skipper, Pablo brings a wealth of knowledge and passion to every journey. Having sailed more than 20,000 nautical miles, including two Atlantic Ocean crossings and a remarkable delivery voyage from Cape Town to the Mediterranean, his career is defined by adventure and expertise.\n\nHis love for the sea is matched by his dedication to safety and precision. Whether guiding charter guests through the stunning Balearic Islands during summer or navigating complex routes, he expertly employs advanced navigational equipment and meticulous planning to ensure smooth and enjoyable voyages.\n\nA natural leader, Pablo thrives on fostering a well-coordinated crew and delivering an exceptional charter experience. With his deep knowledge of weather patterns, local surroundings, and potential challenges, he combines professionalism with a personal passion for sailing, making each trip unforgettable for his guests."},{"name":"Artiz Santiago Ballesteros","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::5dc90960-dcf1-11ef-a54d-2d129dec3260::assets::ebca8850-dcf2-11ef-b0d9-6dd2bd434a6d/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Aritz Ballesteros is a chef renowned for his passion for creating unforgettable culinary experiences. Over the years, he has evolved from a culinary enthusiast into a seasoned Head Chef, excelling in kitchen management, team leadership, menu creation and event organization.\n\nAritz’s career has taken him across much of Europe, including a notable tenure with Chateauform in the Netherlands, where he worked in stunning locations across Holland, Germany, France, and Switzerland. His experience includes positions at prestigious establishments such as the five-star Conservatorium Hotel in Amsterdam and high-end restaurants like Taiko Amsterdam, specializing in Asian cuisine and Helling 7 in Amsterdam.\n\nLast summer, Aritz embraced a new challenge by transitioning to the role of a yacht chef. This career move has been both rewarding and transformative, allowing him to adapt his culinary expertise to the unique demands of working in a confined onboard environment. As a barbecue enthusiast, Aritz has relished the opportunity to innovate while delivering exceptional dining experiences to clients.\n\nHis time in Mallorca was particularly fulfilling, as he consistently exceeded guests' expectations with his culinary artistry. Now based aboard the catamaran Bereshit in the British Virgin Islands, Aritz continues to craft memorable dining experiences for guests exploring the Caribbean.\n\nAlthough he hails from Spain, Aritz’s extensive travels have greatly enriched his culinary repertoire. He remains deeply connected to his Mediterranean roots, specializing in Spanish, Italian, French and Greek cuisines, while skillfully incorporating Asian influences from Japan, Thailand and Indonesia. His appreciation for vibrant flavors also extends to South American cuisines, particularly those of Peru and Mexico.\n\nAritz looks forward to continuing his culinary journey, celebrating the diverse flavours of the world and sharing his innovative creations with guests aboard sailing yacht Bereshit."}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"USD","price":2950000,"displayCurrency":"USD","displayPrice":2950000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricingTo":{"currency":"USD","price":4500000,"displayCurrency":"USD","displayPrice":4500000,"unit":"WEEK"},"pricingInfo":[{"name":"Low Rate","effectiveDates":[],"pricing":{"currency":"USD","charterFee":4500000,"inputAmountTaxed":"EXCLUSIVE","note":"","unit":"WEEK","lineItems":[{"item":"Charter Fee","quantity":2,"unitPrice":2250000,"amount":4500000,"conditions":"VAT and APA Excluded"}],"total":4500000,"subTotal":4500000,"totalTax":0},"inclusionZones":[{"label":"U.S. Virgin Is.","type":"Dependency","category":["North America","Caribbea